Externo
http://0.0.0.0:8082/realms/myrealm/account
Interno
http://keycloak-server:8080/realms/myrealm

Antes de Correr verificar OpenID C en terminal:
docker exec --user www-data owncloud_server occ app:enable openidconnect


docker exec --user www-data owncloud_server occ config:app:set openidconnect openid-connect \
--value='{"provider-url":"http://0.0.0.0:8082/realms/myrealm",
          "client-id":"owncloud",
          "client-secret":"NhVioVp0ZDCUS1YRnE2aFIbt0hPnYXvu",
          "loginButtonName":"LoginA"}'

Finalmente
docker exec --user www-data owncloud_server occ config:app:get openidconnect openid-connect

Para system: 
docker exec --user www-data owncloud_server occ config:list system

Para revisar toda la configuración
docker exec owncloud_server cat /var/www/owncloud/config/config.php